text: Ben Thrash (May 7, 1897 - February 26, 1966) was an American diver. He competed in the men's plain high diving event at the 1924 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1897 births Category:1966 deaths Category:American male divers Category:Olympic divers of the United States Category:Divers at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:People from Frontier County, Nebraska
